2013-08-02  Alexios Ghalanos <alexios@4dscape.com>
	* DESCRIPTION (Version): New version is 1.0-1
	* Added L2 regularization and updated the analytic gradient to take this 
	into account.
	* A number of minor fixes to various functions.
	* Added type argument to residuals with option for deviance, pearson and
	standardized pearson.
	* Added model.matrix, hat and hatvalues (Pregibon  leverage) methods.
	* renamed likelihood method to logLik in keeping with existing 
	stats package convention
	* Added marginal effects, plots etc based on erer package functions maBina
	and maTrend.
	
2013-07-01  Alexios Ghalanos <alexios@4dscape.com>
	* DESCRIPTION (Version): New version is 1.0-0
